- \(P(B_2) = \frac{1}{4}\), \(P(W \mid B_2) = 0\)
- \(P(B_3) = \frac{1}{8}\), \(P(W \mid B_3) = 0.5\)
- \(P(B_4) = \frac{1}{8}\), \(P(W \mid B_4) = 0.75\)

